{
  "stem": "9730.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was, of course, a gradual alienation with my, with my non-Jewish friends and, and classmates.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And whereas, in the beginning, they were almost apologetic about it and saying things such as, well, Hitler doesn't mean people like you, really, or your parents.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you will admit there are certain Jews who really deserve to, you know, to, to get Hitler's wrath and so on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the beginning, they would still be half apologetic about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This soon turned into a real taunting of, of Jewish boys and, and girls.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They might say, you know, there are now some concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And if you don't behave, and you, if you don't watch it, you'll wind up in one of those.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And gradually, they even stop talking to us all together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- but I, I, I could-- I had seen the gradual change of that, also saw how they were exposed to Nazi propaganda.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "For instance, it, it became mandatory for, for all schools and all classes to attend such films as the Leni Riefenstahl film, And I myself had to attend it also.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I could see how, how they were swallowing that up and how, how it affected them and how they were imbued with this idea of German glory.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And anything they would tell them about the Jews, of course, they also swallowed whole.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- so then I remember coming out of this film and seeing, having seen the reaction of my classmates, walking along and, and thinking, how did I get into this position?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why is all this venom directed at me and my family and all the people I know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I, I could see the role that propaganda can play and how it, how it can influence people.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
